551
00:25:22,564 --> 00:25:25,959
Uh... no.
Not really.

552
00:25:26,002 --> 00:25:28,004
But you like her, right?

553
00:25:30,180 --> 00:25:33,357
My daddy says my mommy's job
is to make sure everybody

554
00:25:33,401 --> 00:25:35,490
in that room likes her.

