00:33:06,332 --> 00:33:08,334
in your daughter's
apartment right now.

703
00:33:09,726 --> 00:33:12,207
I'm sorry, you want me
to turn on the television?

704
00:33:12,251 --> 00:33:14,514
Channel three?

705
00:33:14,557 --> 00:33:16,995
Okay.

706
00:33:17,038 --> 00:33:19,606
Uh, Mrs. McCro...

